Create View Identity Column
Main Success Scenario:
  1.Code below
  
      CREATE VIEW [vwWithIdentityCol]
      AS

      WITH CTE AS
      (
        SELECT	DISTINCT Column_Name
        FROM	information_schema.columns
      )
      SELECT	ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Column_Name) - 1 AS ID,  
          Column_Name
      FROM	CTE

      GO
